<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.6.3">
<l>neṟṟimēl kaṇṇāṉum niṟaimoḻivāy nāṉmukaṉum nīṇṭanālvāy</l>
<l>oṟṟaikkai veṇpakaṭṭi ṉoruvaṉaiyu muḷḷiṭṭa vamararōṭum</l>
<l>veṟṟippōrk kaṭalaraiyaṉ viḻuṅkāmal tāṉviḻuṅki yuyyakkoṇṭa</l>
<l>koṟṟappō rāḻiyāṉku ṇamparavāc ciṟutoṇṭar koṭiyavāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Crooked are the ways of small[-minded] servants who do not praise</l>
<l rend="indent">the qualities of the one with the victorious battle discus,</l>
<l>Who took and swallowed the celestials</l>
<l rend="indent">which includes the one with an eye on his forehead,</l>
<l rend="indent">four-faced [Brahmā], his mouths full of words,</l>
<l>And the one on the tall, white elephant with a single limb</l>
<l rend="indent">and a drooping lower lip,</l>
<l>To save them so they were not swallowed by the sea-king,</l>
<l rend="indent">victorious in battle.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
